{
  "stem": "25209.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that would have been, what, '42?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Boy, I tell you, my chronology is going to be a big problem.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we must have been in Korets for a couple of years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's possible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because, as I said, my mother went and tried to get this training.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We would have been in Korets for a couple of years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah, change that one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there are two or three-- yeah, OK.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The next one was Ulyanovsk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now that was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was on the Volga.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's called Ulyanovsk because Lenin was born there, and his-- his original name was Ulyanovsk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was on the Volga.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was the first time that I actually saw ice cream.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Amazing strawberry ice cream you could get.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's where I met-- that's where we ran into, in the street, these people that I was mentioning before, the Altmans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they told us about a Czech army forming in the depth of Russia, and that they were going there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so we did, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't remember much about Ulyanovsk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I have really-- it was-- it was almost like the war hadn't touched it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In other words, you could go to a restaurant and actually order, order a meal.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, there were only two types of meal you could have, [RUSSIAN] or [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[RUSSIAN] is hamburgers, and [RUSSIAN] is stew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But you could go and say, I want this, or I want that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So to me, that was like-- I hadn't-- you know, I had years of not really knowing how life was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was really an amazing break.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think that's where the piano started-- the piano torment started.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a lot of music, and I remember a beautiful garden.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know where we were staying.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
